), and ultimate (yellow) spells.\n-Borazan Visual Upgrade: Borazan's slash effects have been enhanced with improved visuals for a more impactful look.\n-Frost Effect Fix: A visual glitch with the frost status effect on enemies has been resolved for Quest 2 and Quest Pro users.\n-Rune Size Increase: Spell runes have been enlarged for better visibility.\n-Lobby and Shop Improvements: Locked characters and NPCs in the lobby and shops now have a darker appearance for better distinction.\n-Boss Health Bars: Boss health bars have been updated with unique designs for each boss and are now always visible.\n\nGameplay Improvements\n\n-Gesture Drawing: Added sound effects (SFX) and haptic feedback for gesture drawing.\n-Warding Shield SFX: Fixed issues with Warding Shield SFX playing incorrectly.\n-Orange Movement: Fixed an issue with Orange's movement behaviour.\n-Tarkhan Tutorial: Removed the blue screen that occurred after dying and going to the Tarkhan tutorial.\n-Character Consistency: Fixed inconsistencies between Clockwork OranJ and GrumpyuChickenHead.\n-Shop UI: Added spell levels to the shop UI for better information.\n-Enemy Spawning: Fixed an issue that could cause enemies to fall through the environment in the Father tutorial.", "created_date": 1723640409, "id": "7965214593591592", "version": "0.1.3", "version_code": 211, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "7965213163591735"}, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7194998517279874", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8206520296127686"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1723639453, "id": "7965146703598381", "version": "0.1.2